t and evenly distributing body pressure while maintaining flexible comfort.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#110f0f","background_inner":"#000000","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#ffffff","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}},"image_dkxJmK":{"type":"image","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/10_e070c9cd-e0e6-4c21-990a-e7da89aa38d8.png","media_width":50,"media_position":"start","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"Experience Ultimate Comfort and Durability","heading_tag":"h4","content":"<p>The chair reclines from 90° to 160° for customizable comfort, features five quiet casters for smooth mobility, and includes an extendable ottoman for added relaxation. Plus, it’s equipped with an SGS Grade 4 Global Safety Certified gas lift, supporting weights of up to 875 lbs, making it perfect for any user.<\/p>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#110f0f","background_inner":"#000000","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#ffffff","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}},"video_LkVhki":{"type":"video","disabled":true,"settings":{"video":"shopify:\/\/files\/videos\/后仰功能.mp4","external_video_url":"","autoplay":true,"media_width":50,"media_position":"start","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"Recline System","heading_tag":"h4","content":"<ul><li><strong>160° Full Recline<\/strong> – Perfect for gaming, resting or power naps<br\/><\/li><li><strong>Seamless Angle Adjustment<\/strong> – Smooth transition from 90° work mode to 160° relax mode<br\/><\/li><li><strong>Integrated Footrest Compatibility<\/strong> – Full-body support in every position<\/li><\/ul>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#000000","background_gradient":"","text